Project home:
 http://www.appelsiini.net/projects/lazyload
 
Version:  1.5.0
 
 
UPDATE 11 Oct 2011: Cyril (www.yatahonga.com) With the update it really delays the image loading from server (no HTTP request before appearing) and HTML code remains XHTML 1.0 / 1.1 valid

Usage: 
 src: your "preloading" image
 title: URL of the image

Example:
 <img src="img/load.gif" alt="Beautiful Sunrise" title="data/images/sunrise.jpg" />
 
